</p>
<p>Finally, copy the span icon code, remove it, and paste it right <em>after</em> the parent
call, to put this <em>after</em> the widget.</p>
<p>That should do it! Resubmit the form! Got it! One fancy error icon on the name text
field, and zero fancy error icons on the select field.</p>
<p>In a nutshell, form theming means:</p>
<ul>
<li>(A) finding the right block to override and then;</li>
<li>(B) leveraging your variables to do cool stuff.</li>
</ul>
<p>Next, we'll add a missing feature to Symfony: field help text.</p>

    
